<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1h0004-fr-d6730c2d" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Les Entretiens de Confucius</title><editor role="translator">Pierre Ryckmans</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>Les Entretiens de Confucius</title>Paris: Gallimard, 1987</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR1h0004"><title xml:lang="och">論語</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="fr">French</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-01-25T08:47:28.359+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR1h0004-start"><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:47:57.324+09:00">v.12. Zigong dit :</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:48:07.708+09:00">« Je ne veux pas faire à autrui</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:48:12.302+09:00">ce que jene voudrais pas qu'on me fît. »</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:48:25.179+09:00">Le Maître dit :</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:48:46.968+09:00">« Allons donc!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T08:48:49.158+09:00">Tu n’en es pas encore là! »</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:49:55.389+09:00">1.17. Le Maître dit :</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:50:23.672+09:00">« Zilu,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:34:38.262+09:00">je vais t'enseigner ce qu'est le savoir!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:35:36.895+09:00">Le vrai savoir, c'est de reconnaître qu on sait ce qu'on sait,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:51:21.365+09:00">et qu'on ne sait pas ce qu'on ne sait pas. »</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>